edu.uab.ssg.mixomatic.power

Interface BootstrapEstimator.RandomNumberGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomAdapter, RandomAdapter
    Enclosing interface:
    BootstrapEstimator

    public static interface BootstrapEstimator.RandomNumberGenerator
    A random number generator that provides random numbers from the binomial, uniform, and beta distributions; required by the steps of the bootstrap estimation procedure described in the paper.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods
